flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[E264E66C390A6CBB3202881017FD4BB6]", "63CB456D43F9C1474BEFF4B2996AAB5D", "With the preliminary research completed, the trailblazers find themselves a few steps ahead of the competition. The search party makes arrangements to meet back at the nearest town, where settlers have begun to construct the first semblances of a new civilization. As a symbol of hope for the future, they break ground on fertile soil not too far from the edge of Sephilion itself. From that very overlook, the first citizens take in a new view. In the distance, the golden gates of Sephilion peer out of the fog. And the brave and bold might begin to imagine what awaits them just beyond the precipice.")
